sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Deaf User
    participant Mic as Device Microphone
    participant App as HearAlert App (Isolate)
    participant TFLite as AI Inference Engine
    participant Alert as Hardware Dispatcher

    User->>App: Clicks "Start Listening"
    App->>Mic: Request Audio Stream
    loop Continuous Monitoring
        Mic-->>App: Stream 16kHz PCM Buffer
        App->>TFLite: Send Buffer (15,600 samples)
        note over TFLite: Edge Processing (0ms cloud latency)
        TFLite-->>App: Array of Confidences [Fire Alarm: 92%, Siren: 5%]
        
        alt Confidence > Threshold & Not Throttled
            App->>Alert: Trigger Specialized Pattern (e.g. SOS)
            Alert-->>User: Intense Haptic Vibration
            Alert-->>User: Strobe LED Flash
            App-->>User: High-Contrast Screen Takeover
        else Noise or Silence
            App->>App: Discard Frame (Save Battery)
        end
    end
    User->>App: Clicks "Stop Listening"
    App->>Mic: Release Audio Resources
